name: Huson Law Office
overview: Huson Law Office is a Minnesota Law office that specializes in family proceedings such as divorce, spousal maintenance, paternity, child custody, parenting time, child support, antenuptial agreements, and grandparent rights. Huson Law Office knows when you’re going through a hard time and always understands during the sensitive battle of what’s best for your family. That’s why we offer free consolations so you can meet us and be fully informed when you make your choice of family lawyer.
